    • Field Detail

      • student_id

        private int student_id
        Private field student_id, integer without constraints, in SQL database must be unsigned, so sending minus value to SQL database may end SQLException.

      • genGroup

        private java.lang.String genGroup
        Private String genGroup. It's a description of student's place in university: semester or degree. Shouldn't contain forbidden characters like ' or ", which may hack SQL database.

      • attendance

        private Attendance attendance
        Private field attendance, not always initialised, of type Attendance.
